{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"苏区相思柳","authors":["夏天"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":9}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏区相思柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初见相思柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳丝牵我手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崖上锦鸡报晓来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳青青，水悠悠……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思柳哟绿了春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风不肯走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里长渠十里湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里绿柳牵衣袖……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦鸡忙把羽毛抖："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思的春光哪里有？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼春难忘那年头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土家常说春是柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插下柳呵水自来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高岭上能飞舟……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思坡上走来贺老总，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手捏柳枝青悠悠："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟们，栽柳吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天不来不回头……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土司王见柳忙蹬脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手捏龙袍抖几抖："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶小子敢翻天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想引银河坡上流？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土司王，下毒手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着绿柳把刀丢……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位将军山上立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支柳树把芽抽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杆红旗出山来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片杀声如雷吼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦鸡从此开歌喉："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有贺龙，就有相思柳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了柳呵春似酒："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坝上、渠边、寨门口……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳成荫，柳林秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳枝拂水似挥手——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东到背背崖，西到狮子口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里云湖鱼竞游；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南到姊妹坡，北到凤凰岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金鹿、羊群唱不休……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳絮年年飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军心不走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春三二月抚柳条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象是握着贺总的手……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}